6 payment,
7 d. tax liability of the taxpayer from any prior tax year,
8 or
9 e. any debt, unpaid fine, final judgment, or claim filed
10 with the Commission by a qualified entity as defined
11 in Section 205.2 of Title 68 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
